*Bravo* mu je rekao šef nakon uspešne prezentacije. (He was congratulated by his boss after successful presentation).

Kad je video njegovu izvedbu, publika je počela da viče: *Bravo*! (When they saw his performance, the audience started to shout "Bravo!").

*Bravo* ti, uspeo si da postigneš svoj cilj. (Bravo to you, you managed to reach your goal).

Ona je zaista *bravo* izvela svoju ulogu. (She really did a great job in her role).

*Bravo* za tvoj uspeh! (Bravo for your success!).